## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not capture all perspectives on the implications of globalization on job searching. The rapidly changing nature of globalization and its impact on the job market means that new trends and data may emerge that are not covered in this report. Additionally, the report primarily focuses on the implications for developed countries, and the effects may differ in developing regions.